[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    441[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mAmazon QuickSight for operational and quality dashboards.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m Per-participant encoding rate, per-cycle linkage-rate trend, per-cohort linkage-rate disparity, salt-rotation cadence and coverage, parameterization-upgrade adoption, consent-withdrawal volume, re-encoding backlog, and audit-volume trends.[K
